        "17401370328482839826": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "About Us – PKCabinets",
            "title_size": "medium"
          },
          "blockId": "17401370328482839826"
        },
        "1740137032848c18dc0e": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>In an era of fast-paced living and the need for efficiency, <strong>PKCabinets</strong>&nbsp;has risen quietly in the heart of America to provide top-notch home improvement solutions. Whether you're a budget-conscious business or an innovative DIY enthusiast, we're here to meet your needs and provide a one-stop kitchen and bathroom remodeling solution that ensures every customer enjoys superior quality and convenience in the most cost-effective way possible.</p>"
          },
          "blockId": "1740137032848c18dc0e"
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
