      "blocks": {
        "174013704684042bf0cd": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Our Mission",
            "title_size": "medium"
          },
          "blockId": "174013704684042bf0cd",
          "sectionId": "17401370468405e1f08a",
          "canAddBlock": true,
          "formatName": "Our Mission",
          "overLimit": true
        },
        "174013704684016328f8": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Operating through a factory direct network, PK Cabinet allows you to purchase high-quality home furnishings products directly from the factory at factory prices, eliminating the middleman and extra costs. We're especially known for our signature <strong>Shaker style</strong>, which has won acclaim for its simplicity, timeless appeal and versatility. Whether you're renovating your kitchen or remodeling your bathroom, PK Cabinet is the perfect choice.</p>"
          },
          "blockId": "174013704684016328f8",
          "custom_css": [],
          "sectionId": "17401370468405e1f08a",
          "canAddBlock": true,
          "formatName": "文本",
