        "174013704684042bf0cd": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Our Commitment",
            "title_size": "medium"
          },
          "blockId": "174013704684042bf0cd",
          "sectionId": "1742208173048970f48d",
          "canAddBlock": true,
          "formatName": "Our Commitment",
          "overLimit": true
        },
        "174013704684016328f8": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>As our style options continue to expand, PK Cabinet maintains our core commitment to <strong>providing fast, cost-effective renovations without compromising on quality.</strong>&nbsp;We are more than just a home furnishing company, we are committed to creating functional and beautiful living spaces that give you confidence and satisfaction on every home renovation journey.</p>"
