      },
      "blocks": {
        "174013704684042bf0cd": {
          "type": "title",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Our Team",
            "title_size": "medium"
          },
          "blockId": "174013704684042bf0cd",
          "sectionId": "17422082039933a40534",
          "canAddBlock": true,
          "formatName": "Our Team",
          "overLimit": true
        },
        "174013704684016328f8": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>At PK Cabinet, we don't just rely on technical and product strengths, we have a passionate and creative team. Our team consists of experienced designers, professional craftsmen and efficient customer service staff who are dedicated to providing unparalleled home solutions to every customer.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>- Designers</strong></p>\n<p>Our designers translate your ideas and needs into specific design solutions, ensuring that every cabinet and bathroom fixture fits your aesthetic and usage needs. They understand the uniqueness of each space and specialize in design solutions that combine creativity and practicality to transform your home.</p>\n<p><strong>- Craftsmen and Manufacturing Team</strong></p>\n<p>Every PK Cabinet product is handcrafted by experienced craftsmen to ensure that every cabinet and bathroom fixture is flawless. Our craftsmen take every technical detail to the extreme and strive for the best.</p>\n<p><strong>- Customer Service Team</strong></p>\n<p>We understand that the needs of our customers are of paramount importance, so we place special emphasis on communication and service with our customers. Whether it's during the design phase or post-installation, our customer service team is always on hand to provide expert advice and support to ensure your home renovation experience is smooth and worry-free.</p>"
          },
          "blockId": "174013704684016328f8",
          "custom_css": [],
          "sectionId": "17422082039933a40534",
